{{!--
  om-discovery.hbs — renders .well-known/open-membership as JSON.

  Ghost renders Handlebars templates as the body of the response.
  routes.example.yaml sets content_type: application/json for this path.

  As with om-feed.hbs, this template is the Mode A fallback. In Mode B the
  sidecar serves the discovery document from service/discovery.ts so that
  the JSON can be generated programmatically from om-config.yaml + Stripe
  rather than from static Handlebars.

  The `om_discovery` helper (registered by om-ghost) returns a JSON-
  serialisable object matching the SPEC §9 shape.
--}}
